Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:09.92,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going now, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.27,0:00:17.77,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:18.81,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:23.06,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time, can you rent these DVDs from Wataru's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:27.31,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I will. It's cold today, so take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.67,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No worries. The battle plan is already made.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.07,0:00:34.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It really is cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:36.88,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.64,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, eyes front! The wind will hit me directly, otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.68,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:47.53,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're very clever, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:51.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Hinagiku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.68,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, spacing out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:01.27,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Something was on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:07.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that the Superintendent, the walking hazard producer, started something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:10.92,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. The Superintendent should be down on a southern island, enjoying her vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.11,0:01:27.60,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzuha-sama, say "Ah..."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:35.70,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have to come all the way here just to eat rice cakes, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:38.08,Default,Kuz,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the sake of good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:41.55,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then what could be bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:45.00,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Onee-chan gave me a New Year's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.06,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:47.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-sensei gave you a New Year's allowance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.97,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,She came over yesterday and left this on my desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.40,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Although, there was only ¥500 inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:58.03,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,¥500?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.03,Default-alt,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that little?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:00.67,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That's a fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:03.32,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I've only gotten azuki beans or peanuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.25,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:12.48,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there. If you chitchat too long, you'll be late to school. {ep 40}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.90,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to arrest you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:15.11,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Bad boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.92,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's totally different from usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:26.16,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Did you all know there's a huge mansion like this in the middle of Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.75,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the mistress who lives there is Sanzenin Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.66,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.63,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Her butler's name is Ayasaki Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:35.63,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The two are slightly airheaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.04,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...and they misunderstand each other a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.04,0:02:43.19,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...but are bound by a tight master-butler bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:45.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,K-Katsura-sensei is acting differently than usual! {ep 40}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.91,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,She looks dazzling. {ep 40}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.75,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.08,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, you three?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No, how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.59,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Your total change is getting to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:39.09,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you perhaps eat grass\Nfrom the turf or a laughing mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:40.75,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:42.29,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,"Why?" Obviously that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:49.20,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... It's just that today's a very special day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Special day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:54.78,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,The morning staff meeting is coming up soon, so I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.12,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:10.42,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-chan's quitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.97,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:17.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.29,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's totally impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.98,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji would never quit being a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:26.10,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Where would she live if she quits from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,But she's been acting strangely since this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:32.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,and she said today's a special day or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,and she even gave Hinagiku-san a New Year's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:39.28,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's planning to quit from Hakuou\Nand go somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:41.27,Default,3,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:44.72,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,If what you said is true, I'll go shave my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.38,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change my name to Men Taiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:47.38,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Mentaiko = Spicy egg roe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:51.82,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll change this anime's title to Yamabiko no Gotoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:51.82,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Yamabiko = The echo you hear back in the mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.82,0:05:53.03,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.30,0:05:58.53,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you actually saw her letter of resignation, then I'd be convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:05:59.64,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.53,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.20,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,It was true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.65,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,If you had picked it up, you should have said so!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:20.34,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:22.21,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.81,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to call it quits as a teacher, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.83,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,It's a prank, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.83,0:06:26.00,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us it's a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:29.97,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, calling it quits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.28,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.18,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Today's the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.25,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Today?! Isn't that too sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.51,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It was a little hard to bring it up with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.59,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You're joking right, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:47.83,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.74,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What is there to do after one quits being a teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.53,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of things to do out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:59.07,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a journey or even start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.97,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why did you not tell such an important thing to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.52,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Katsura-chan. You're being such a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.24,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:09.87,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you even ask for a little advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:13.71,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fully-grown adult, so why should I come looking for advice for something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:19.04,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's a conclusion that was reached after much thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.33,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.62,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for surprising you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.42,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:31.88,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbyes come suddenly and unannounced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.24,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, life is filled with sudden goodbyes. {ep 40}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.27,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never find dandelions in the winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:48.88,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Marilla, when you're truly sad, tears don't come, do they? 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.88,Default-alt,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Sudden goodbyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:55.71,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, I'll never leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:07:57.34,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Matthew. {Anne of Green Gables. Anyone with quote?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.44,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But not a single tear is coming out. {Anne of Green Gables. Anyone with quote?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.73,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, Onee-chan! {ep 40}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:02.91,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about you! {ep 40}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.53,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,You can go die on the street of nowhere! {ep 40}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hinagiku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:10.17,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:42.77,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hina. It's about time you came home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:50.34,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at how much New Year's allowance I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I got some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:54.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is from Daddy, and this is Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:57.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This is from Grandma, and this is Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:08:59.95,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.40,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:05.33,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that I haven't given you your New Year's allowance yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:06.57,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Stick your hand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:09.89,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:16.16,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to let me off the hook with that this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:22.92,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, I'll never leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:24.04,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.34,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, full course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.48,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a piggy back ride, so let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.35,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.90,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.84,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Rukkorasetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.84,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Rukkorasetto = Up I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.81,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Toshi niha katenai none.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.81,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Toshi niha katenai none = Looks like you can't beat growing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.84,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought Katsura-chan would really quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.63,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.89,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Despite everything we've done to her,\Nshe's taken care of us a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:17.10,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,How do we fight against homework and tests from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:20.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone's very shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.17,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:26.27,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,This is too much to be one of her spur of the moment things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but the truth is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:34.79,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could attend one more of her world history classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:35.78,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.54,0:10:43.79,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Right, the next homeroom period will be the goodbye with Katsura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:47.63,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, homeroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:54.80,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,We'll now start the homeroom period.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.20,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, today's agenda is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:00.29,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Katsura-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:05.50,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question regarding the rise and fall of the Frankish Empire, so could you give a lecture?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:10.52,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,I request the Reconquista events that happened in Spain during the Middle Ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:13.12,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,What were the four historically important apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.99,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true Pythagoras was allergic to horse beans?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:20.65,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that an Englishman invented the ready-made curry pack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:24.07,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We have so many more questions, so please answer them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.28,Default-alt,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.33,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:29.49,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:32.94,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to enjoy Yukiji's last class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.84,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, this is an important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.79,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,1806, Continental Blockade!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.74,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:45.72,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura-sensei's lecture goes at a good tempo as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:48.62,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like a she doesn't have herself together, but she's actually good at teaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:52.02,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did you know that Napoleon was into fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:55.37,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,She even tells us things you don't learn from textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:12:00.78,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a simple thing where you hold a coin\Nin your left hand and flip a crepe in the frying pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.77,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,He did that five times and failed the fifth one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:08.75,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,This was in 1812. The year the French invasion of Russia failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:08.14,Default-alt,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,After this class...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.62,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be able to experience it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:27.06,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,This is important, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.65,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you review it from your textbook later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:36.42,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the reason Napoleon keeps his right hand in pocket is-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:38.24,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you crying, Segawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.20,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:46.03,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't tears. It's hot water from last night's bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:47.21,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:55.23,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. So you've all finally understood that history is made with tears on top of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.12,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Meetings and farewells. And then yet another meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:01.47,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,The links between people are what make history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.72,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:06.74,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,The character "people" is made\Nwith two people supporting each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.34,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! People can't live alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:11.90,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.01,Default,Other,0000,0000,0000,,Live alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:19.76,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,If Onee-chan were to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.37,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,No one in this world lives alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:29.62,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they are far apart,\Nthey're always connected by their hearts. 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.52,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.06,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I want you all to understand that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.16,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.69,0:13:38.24,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Tears are the sweat your heart perspires.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:41.03,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,And love is the work your heart does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:47.74,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,That's the end of the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.97,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.40,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.16,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't quit, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.34,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many more things we want to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.34,0:14:08.73,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,So many more things we want to do, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.37,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:13.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,If you leave, my life-threatening experiences will decrease, and it won't be as enjoyable as it has been!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.51,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:19.35,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still plan to leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:22.62,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,At least stay until we graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.44,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Please promise us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.91,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,"Promise?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:29.75,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.18,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.18,Default-alt,All,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! Don't quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.98,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.88,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to know that you all cared about me so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:46.94,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Being a teacher was so much harder than I'd thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.02,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. And there's one more shop to visit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:57.00,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Please get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:15:00.48,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,So I gave my letter of resignation to Katsura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.31,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Letter of resignation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:03.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.70,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.70,0:15:09.06,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I forgot to turn it in to the Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:10.92,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:18.48,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing your class, I was able to learn how amazing the bond between students and teachers can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:23.03,Default,Mak,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Forgive me for not noticing your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:24.97,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.90,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,This is so touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:29.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:30.91,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:35.50,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, we're having a storm of "Why?" in the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.33,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,Were you quitting, Yukiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:40.92,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:46.19,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then what was the unnatural dazzling smiley aura you were emitting from the morning about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:50.23,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that'd be because it's been such a lucky day since the moment I woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.50,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:00.74,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki Nobuko-sensei's fortune telling for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:03.96,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! You Scorpios have the best luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:07.91,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Especially those who are of blood type B,\Nlove alcohol, and have a long pinky toe nail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:10.35,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,It's your luckiest day that comes only once every twelve years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:13.55,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,None of this is ever true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.06,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The tea stalk is standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:18.72,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Twin egg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.69,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,They all have eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:21.96,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,It's the angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:24.33,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,D-Double red sea bream!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.25,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it went!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.90,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.82,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me so happy, super happy, out of my mind, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.64,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.82,0:16:34.77,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Look at these. These are the proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:38.07,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder Napoleon believed in fortune telling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:49.05,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for all the confusing reactions my stupid sister has caused!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.24,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we jumped the gun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:56.04,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew something was strange from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.77,Default,Izu,0000,0000,0000,,What were all the tears we shed for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.87,Default,Mik,0000,0000,0000,,You will have to make up for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.50,Default,Ris,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do fifty years worth of our homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.50,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.38,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never believe in fortune telling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:14.41,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the unwed female teacher's heart rotted further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:21.32,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then what's the meaning behind her giving Hinagiku-san the New Year allowance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.91,0:17:23.76,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,The mystery to that has been already solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:29.95,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, why don't you all just bring spears or guns for all I care, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:29.49,Default-alt,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}She really needs so much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:41.53,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,One day, I will actually give you\Na New Year's allowance, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.26,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,When is "one day?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:44.85,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.08,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I don't have much confidence that I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.66,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.16,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.50,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely give you one ten years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:15.34,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, Pirates of the Beach and Man Spider 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:16.07,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.71,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:21.59,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Remind Nagi to pay attention to the return date.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.20,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.08,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:27.48,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Please take these with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:28.66,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:32.49,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry. My grandmother sent a whole bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:36.46,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Th-These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.82,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,These are still being manufactured?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:42.36,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, where is Saki-san's grandmother now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:42.83,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.36,0:18:47.10,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:52.59,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,While I couldn't decide if I should send a New Year's card to Hayate-kun or not, the New Year's already come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:58.58,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, didn't I set this year's resolution to become a mature woman with confidence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.17,0:19:03.22,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:04.64,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.36,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:09.66,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,You picking a fight with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:13.57,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Am I going to be killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me? I'll beat you up or else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be dead meat if you look down on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:21.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nerve picking a fight with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:21.33,Default-alt,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I always fall into pinches like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.68,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right, you are Nishizawa-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:28.36,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun's friend, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:32.02,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for letting Nagi sleep over last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:33.52,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:39.26,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,As you can tell, she's a difficult girl in some ways, but I hope you'll be good friends with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.69,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.14,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, who might these people be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:46.08,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Are they your friends, Nishizawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.27,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Why does it look like that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:49.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.05,0:19:55.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you're a little cute maid, don't try to ignore us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:02.28,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I don't understand the Cre*in language.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.24,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,We're speaking Japanese, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:08.89,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,If you look down on us, even if you're a cute maid, we won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:22.47,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite inelegant to try to grab a female's chest without cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:26.54,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,A simple self-defense move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:29.79,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Although, I can only use it as a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get off the hook now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.78,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.67,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You will not leave with just injuries otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.08,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:47.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:48.83,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.79,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:52.56,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.03,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,On another note, this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:55.93,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:59.40,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,T-Th-This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.71,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:07.73,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this will be a good year for you, Nishizawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:11.02,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah. If you'd like, take this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:14.59,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:32.80,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Nishizawa-san wishes to become like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:37.15,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Did anything new happen at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:38.71,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.04,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.31,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:49.75,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why. All of a sudden I feel like eating marshmallows.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:54.69,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next week, we'll fight against sine, cosine, and tangent.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.36,0:23:31.94,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Katsura Yukiji's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.94,0:23:33.61,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:36.89,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there. It's your sexy teacher, Katsura Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:40.48,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everyone; my character song is finally done!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:44.85,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,I got nervous over my first recording,\Nbut I did my best for the sake of my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:46.40,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.66,0:23:48.15,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hina, you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.15,0:23:49.80,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:52.74,Default,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,We rehearsed last night regarding what to do here together, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:53.93,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:58.08,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, Hina's singing in my song, too, so make sure you buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.65,Default,Kat,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:23:59.65,Default-alt,Hin,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:03.18,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Does he have any weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.18,0:24:04.47,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Weaknesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.47,0:24:08.49,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Manga or anime main characters usually come with weaknesses as a default setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.49,0:24:09.96,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Do they?
